  "texts": [
    "A Q&A evaluation dataset for breast cancer nursing care was collected from publicly available datasets and nurses at a tertiary hospital.",
    "A total of 200 Q&A pairs were included in this study following manual selection by two nurses with more than 10 years of work experience, through the application of stringent inclusion and exclusion criteria.",
    "During the final evaluation, 15 questions were selected using a computer randomization method (LZZ, Python software).",
    "Each question was sent to the GPT-4 and RAG-GPT groups, and the final responses were recorded.",
    "The inclusion criteria were as follows: (1) questions related to breast cancer medical care, nursing, or rehabilitation and (2) questions with accurate answers."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}